\mathbb{F}_p[x]
\displaystyle\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{N_p(n)}{p^n},
n
\mathbb{F}_p[x]
N_p(n)=\frac{1}{n}\sum_{d|n}p^d\mu\left(\frac{n}{d}\right)
\frac{1}{n}.
n
p^{n/2}
\sum_{d|n} p^n\mu\left(\frac{n}{d}\right)=p^n+O\left(np^{n/2}\right),
\frac{nN_p(n)}{p^{n}}=1+O\left(n^2p^{-n/2}\right),
\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\frac{nN_p(n)}{p^{n}}=1.
